---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Editorial Policy — AI Zest"
  description="Our editorial standards, review policies, and commitment to honest, unbiased AI tool reviews."
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-8 sm:py-12">
    
    <!-- Breadcrumb -->
    <nav class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-1.5 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-[#3B82F6]">Home</a>
      <span>/</span>
      <span class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white font-medium">Editorial Policy</span>
    </nav>

    <!-- Hero -->
    <div class="text-center mb-10">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-[#3B82F6] to-[#8B5CF6] text-white text-2xl mb-4">
        📝
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">
        Editorial <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-[#3B82F6] to-[#8B5CF6]">Policy</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Our commitment to honest, transparent, and independent AI tool reviews.
      </p>
      <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 mt-2">Last updated: June 24, 2026</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Content -->
    <div class="prose prose-gray dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
      
      <h2>Our Independence</h2>
      <p>AI Zest operates independently. We are not owned by, funded by, or affiliated with any of the AI tools we review. Our editorial decisions are made solely by our team, based on our research, testing, and analysis.</p>
      <p>No company can pay for a positive review, a higher rating, or placement on our Best Of lists. We maintain full editorial control over all content published on the site.</p>

      <h2>How We Select Tools for Review</h2>
      <p>We select tools based on:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Popularity and search demand</strong> — tools that users are actively searching for</li>
        <li><strong>Industry significance</strong> — tools that represent meaningful innovations in their category</li>
        <li><strong>Reader requests</strong> — we welcome suggestions from our audience</li>
        <li><strong>Market relevance</strong> — tools that solve real problems for our readers</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We strive to cover both well-established platforms and emerging tools that show promise. Being listed on AI Zest does not imply endorsement — every tool receives an objective rating based on our methodology.</p>

      <h2>Review Methodology</h2>
      <p>Every tool on AI Zest is evaluated using our <a href="/how-we-review">consistent, transparent methodology</a>. Each tool receives a rating out of 5.0 across five equally-weighted dimensions: Feature Completeness, Pricing & Value, Ease of Use, Performance & Quality, and Support & Community.</p>
      <p>Our reviews are based on hands-on testing whenever possible. For tools we cannot fully test (e.g., enterprise-only platforms), we rely on thorough research, expert consultations, and verified user feedback.</p>

      <h2>Affiliate Disclosure</h2>
      <p>Some links on AI Zest are affiliate links. When you click an affiliate link and make a purchase, we may earn a commission at no additional cost to you. This is a standard practice across the review and directory industry.</p>
      <p><strong>Critically, affiliate relationships never influence our ratings, reviews, or placement.</strong> We do not accept payment for higher ratings, featured placement, or positive reviews. Our affiliate partners have no input into our editorial content.</p>
      <p>We clearly identify affiliate links with a disclosure notice on every page where they appear.</p>

      <h2>Corrections Policy</h2>
      <p>We strive for accuracy in every review and article. If you identify an error — whether in pricing, features, ratings, or factual claims — please <a href="/contact">contact us</a>. We aim to review and correct errors within 2 business days. Significant corrections are noted at the bottom of the affected page.</p>

      <h2>Sponsored Content</h2>
      <p>AI Zest does not accept sponsored reviews or paid placements that influence editorial content. Any sponsored or promotional content would be clearly labeled as such. As of June 2026, we have no sponsored content on the site.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions about this policy? <a href="/contact">Get in touch</a>.</p>

    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
